Other approaches, which are more for intermediate+ players, use  TRANSFER BIDS, we'll discuss those in upcoming lessons too.


Please just remember, if you are playing with an unknown partner - the most IMPORTANT thing is to agree whether you play NATURAL or TRANSFER responses after a 1NT opening. 
For now we will learn the natural responses, until you have more practice, these are easier to understand.
But in the future we'll overtake transfer responses, as that is MOST COMMON on BBO in Basic Sayc|
