^b@2Let's take a look at responders next strength category: (2) 9-10 points
With 9-10 TP hands the partnership has a combined strength of 24-27 points.  
Half of time there is 26-27 points therefore responder needs more information.

For that we use the 2NT response: that asks opener to tell how many points he has.
In our examples, Responder 2 bids 2NT  as an INVITATIONAL bid|
