at|

- With 15 HCP opener passes, and we play with 24-25 TP a 2NT part score.|
pg| ***** 26 ***** |


at| 

- With 16-17 points opener bids 3NT, and we play a (25)26-27 TP Golden Game.|
pg| ***** 27 ***** |


at|

Therefore we call 2NT an INVITATIONAL bid - opener may pass or bid on, depending on his strength.
Look at Opener's hand again: If his partner invites him with 2NT he must choose PASS, as he has only 15 HCP|
